N2  - In this paper we obtain the Laplace-Stieltjes transform of the time an arriving customer spends in an FBN queueing system until completion of service at the kth level (1 ? k ? N) given that at least k levels of service are required. The results are conditioned upon the state of the system at the time of arrival of the customer.
